Package: GeneScout
Title: De Novo Small ORF Discovery with Entropy Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-01-20
Authors@R: 
    person("Dany", "Mukesha", , "danymukesha@gmail.com", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-9514-751X"))
Description: A toolkit for identifying hidden genes in non-coding DNA using
    statistical information theory. Implements sliding window entropy scanning,
    Shannon entropy calculation, and Kullback-Leibler divergence to discover
    potential small open reading frames (ORFs) in genomic sequences without 
    requiring prior annotation. Fills the gap between existing codon usage 
    bias tools and de novo gene discovery in non-coding regions.
